text: Sarah Connolly (born 1963) is an English mezzo-soprano. Sarah Connolly may also refer to one of the following: *Sarah A. Connolly, American virologist *Sarah Connolly (politician), Australian Labor Party politician *Sarah Sugden (also Connolly), fictional character in British soap opera Emmerdale ==See also== *Sarah O'Connell (1822?–1870), New Zealand runholder
title: Sarah Connolly (disambiguation)
